{"type": "article", "id": 10392, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-06-04T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2112, "name": "针孔照相机"}, {"id": 34, "name": "自行车"}, {"id": 11065, "name": "可视化天气预报器"}, {"id": 1531, "name": "帽子"}, {"id": 3704, "name": "鞋子"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 11066, "name": "Miansai"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235552bkXgLOn71xQcJaEo.png", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tA Pinhole Camera by ONDU\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tONDU 一直致力于针孔照相机的设计和制作，最近他们推出了一系列针孔照相机。相机所有的木制材均取自当地森林里面的胡桃木和枫木，表面涂有设计师自己制作的蜂蜡和天然油脂的混合物，用作一个保护层。此外，相机使用磁铁作为连接固定。目前，他们正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，如果对针孔照相机感兴趣，不妨<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ondu-/ondu-pinhole-cameras-mk-ii/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140556ijdnV4N8yQEuwYpR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140556v58XsNO9CZyaASMc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140556ZpVa3W0D2GE5yCw9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140557vCRKqDbgazcNVxP3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140557Bs1t38EwmHqYNgIl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405584Ef8kaiohHuv2P7b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405588kOoKqHn3QLXmA2F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405584ub3rGOWUyEiZPFq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34107579\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tCity Cycle by Tokyobike x Ace Hotel\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">时尚旅馆 Ace Hotel 和日本自行车品牌 Tokyobike 最近联手推出了一个自行车系列，此前他们曾经合作为 Ace Hotel 推出租赁款式，供住客租借。此次他们在之前款式的基础上进行了调整，变成了一个买走的自行车。这个系列中所有自行车配色都轻松明快，充满浓浓夏日风情，就像是加州的阳光和欧洲色缤纷色彩。目前自行车售价 875 美元，在洛杉矶和伦敦的 Ace Hotel 都可以买到，<a href=\"http://shop.acehotel.com/products/tokyobike\" target=\"_blank\">这是线上购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140559NBasdHcQ91Ox5Zbz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061405593TNbcg2jXKxDpOzV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140600D1VjzNeyKUrO9qWl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140600nI7C3KPc2uwYG840.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140601zfHEKdsUVnwyTCMS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">Tempescope by Ken Kawamoto</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">来自日本的 Ken Kawamoto 先生设计了一个浪漫的天气预报器，这个叫做 Tempescope 的小立方体可以让你坐在房间里实时便可直观地观测到第二天的天气。只要和智能手机相连，小盒子就既能刮风下雨，又可以万里无云，风和日丽。Tempescope 由 Ken Kawamoto 先生和他的团队耗时数年完成，计划将于今年内登陆 Kickstarter 进行众筹。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140602ZDsadM2epAwbk05J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140602GXfL2ydNDZcuplvC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55568182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140602Q1j6DGU4pqonbcR2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75113636\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140603L6xiUK8GbqWF7JHp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75113636\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140603p1z46jL7xgtNvFno.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.06590909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140604OqpI7HJQisLgZN5V.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5631769\" data-format=\"gif\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140605c3pTJZ7NlbivkzuX.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">Pokémon by BEAMS &amp; New Era</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">日本经典游戏《Pokémon》即将迎来其 20 岁生日，为此其官方邀请 BEAMS 和 New Era 联手推出了一个帽子系列，其设计主题是广受全世界人们喜爱的皮卡丘。在配色上，选用了皮卡丘经典黄色以及海军蓝色，趣味盎然。产品将于本月末上市。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614060617BYht4plAvxEHgu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140606bpsmUqcR7yP5re6V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140607aAjhlJCpevQnIHZY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140608iEpZtQSsRcCFVAHr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66410256\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">Bags by Miansai </span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">珠宝与手表品牌 Miansai 最近开始涉足包袋领域，推出了一系列包袋产品，包括背包，手提包，旅行包，钱包等各种款式。包袋的设计秉承其珠宝和手表设计的精致气质，配色上选用棕色，绿色，海军蓝，咖啡色，黑色等稳重的颜色，看起来质感十足。<a href=\"http://www.miansai.com/shop/bags\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140608Efy9n8vc0KdzA67T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061406088sBnvfCTPMRHKg0L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140609iHWkaYTKNfeMtbp9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140609oM0k1WYVAvE5Nyhm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">New Superstar by Adidas</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t <span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\">Adidas 月初推出其经典鞋款 Superstar 复古进阶版，仍然选用全白色的皮革，搭配了其经典三道杠斜紋麂皮标识，鞋头保留了 Superstar 经典的贝壳样式。目前鞋子有三种颜色可选，分别是红白配色，黑白配色和深蓝与白配色。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140610XjNnkfw6ZhISRoti.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140610XWivOVsZ7fNKp6Iu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140610niJW5d4xob3mpGDK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}